{"id": "1220813116430876762", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "海渊之力（狂气爆发）", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T19:15:28.568000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220813112694014022", "filename": "Image_1711134690737.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1174208, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220813112694014022/Image_1711134690737.png?ex=69ccc60f&is=69cb748f&hm=dc65b1f779be4c85c2fa72f816e44fb3b3cf315756ab57ac9822abefc1121f04&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220813342416048309", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "巨刃之威（衍生卡）", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T19:16:22.447000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220813341828714536", "filename": "Image_1711134676145.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1208771, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220813341828714536/Image_1711134676145.png?ex=69ccc646&is=69cb74c6&hm=0e1c1112b54a45f00508363cd20496ef1a7887bd87f2bd17e43949420dac1ce3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220814745964380261", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "因为是晚上突发奇想研究这写文字写了什么，拉着程序A用感人的视力仔细研究了一下，并通过查阅克苏鲁语词典和拉莱耶翻译器等资源，我们得出了以下内容（按上面展示顺序）：", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T19:21:57.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220818169514426399", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "①图鲁\n1.深渊号令\n以之前已经得到的字母，只差前两个字母没有出现。根据角色战斗语音【技能·一：天罚！】，推测出之前并没有出现的字母，为punished（惩罚）的前两个字母：p和u。\n\n2.星辰正位之刻\n即使加入p和u，已知的字母依旧很少，但是我们的程序A根据结构找到了克总颂词，也就是原文：\n\nPh'nglui mglw'nafh Cthulhu R'lyeh wgah'nagl fhtagn\n（在永恒的宅邸拉莱耶中，长眠的克苏鲁候汝入梦）\n\n个人对克苏鲁神话系列并没有深入研究，只在此放上涉及到克总的相关咒文。通神、降临，也是一种正位之刻。珊或许就是这样沉迷于此的。\n\n（蓝色字为本次新增字母）", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T19:35:33.317000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:05:05.899000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220818168973627544", "filename": "Image_1711135427363.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 92803, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220818168973627544/Image_1711135427363.png?ex=69cccac5&is=69cb7945&hm=bf653fcb892dd39cdae8b820fa616b9deacdf07a07a65b1dec5deeb24c034008&"}, {"id": "1220818169296326697", "filename": "Image_1711135963992.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 73388, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220818169296326697/Image_1711135963992.jpg?ex=69cccac5&is=69cb7945&hm=ae1a9ab218dfbe1fbfc0499631168caa5b3be68f69989fec2d052186014094b3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220824383640309851", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "②墨菲\n1.螺湮逆流\n技能特效上的文字【li’hee】是拉莱耶语，翻译过来就是【以……的方式处罚】。\n墨菲的这个技能，笼统的说，和图鲁深渊号令比较相似，对所有敌人造成伤害+触腕攻击，被戏称为“小天罚”。\n战斗语音【技能·一：尝尝教训！】也符合惩罚的意思。\n\n2.虚妄继承者\n狂气爆发的文字看起来很多，其实只有一个单词在反复利用，也就是【phantasmal】，形容词，意思有幻影的、空想的。具体释义见图。", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:00:14.880000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:00:52.564000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220824383002775714", "filename": "Image_1711136674145.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 50015, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220824383002775714/Image_1711136674145.png?ex=69ccd08e&is=69cb7f0e&hm=08733783ef9edb4c1e2ab88d410b85ca2006aede3de7b58ed4515ee4a16a1ba8&"}, {"id": "1220824383224938516", "filename": "Image_1711137200387.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 204733, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220824383224938516/Image_1711137200387.jpg?ex=69ccd08e&is=69cb7f0e&hm=77ba7f9e47eadd44419f004f49d8d0bc570c0666e4d0596f75855f4746c19e82&"}, {"id": "1220824383438721147", "filename": "Image_1711136642482.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 67408, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220824383438721147/Image_1711136642482.jpg?ex=69ccd08e&is=69cb7f0e&hm=4bce17e63ba3e5996296751dddc7a75e66c2b78e7509dd055f0839f20eac27a5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220829247988568094", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "经过克总大放送，接下来对照简单很多。\n\n③法洛思\n深邃暗流\n虽然技能特效有偷懒的嫌疑……总之特效文字显示的是拉莱耶语【grah’n】，翻译过来是【失落者，潜在仆从，幼体、幼虫】。\n该技能的故事文本为：\n趋光本能让飞虫追逐着光亮，而那长明灯火又过于灼目，让人往往忽略了水面下暗流的汹涌……\n\n而法洛思本人也经历了永恒之国的沉没。在故事·三中有表述，“永恒之国的倾塌沉没，于法洛思而言就像城楼失去了地基，藤蔓失去了土壤。对永恒之国的信仰支撑着她在世间浮游，但久寻不见的哀苦与无尽的孤独最终压垮了可怜的旅人。”\n法洛思对故国思念成狂，而永恒之国早已失落不再，成为历史的尘埃。", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:19:34.631000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:17:57.036000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220829247799562241", "filename": "Image_1711138107942.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 4946, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220829247799562241/Image_1711138107942.jpg?ex=69ccd516&is=69cb8396&hm=2d24e02f834985a83c409adec2325be8f9be1dd5f2a0905278a326de9c78a11e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220832015444873328", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168855337609199728", "author_name": "anachico", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~眼睛快给我看瞎了，们守密人大晚上不睡觉都是在干什么呢~~", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:30:34.444000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220837705429291091", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "戈利亚用到的文字技能特效比较多，其中含义主要涉及他的原型大衮（达贡）。当然也有毫无情趣的英文单词。\n\n④戈利亚\n1.复仇预行\n【revenge】复仇，报仇。\n非常直白，没什么可说的。\n\n2.强者为尊\n这个技能写的比较有意思，直接使用了戈利亚的名字“Goliat”作为“强者”，当然这也很符合人物本身。\n不过，在英文中“巨人”的单词是【Goliath】，这个掉了h的单词也可以指代“巨人歌利亚”，不过并非英语。\n个人对语言学并不十分了解，只通过搜索得知在西班牙语的巨人写法是【Goliat】，指代的同样是传说中的巨人歌利亚。\n具体是避嫌，还是取自非英语单词，这得看官方怎么说.jpg", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T20:53:11.042000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:16:55.994000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220837704598818857", "filename": "Image_1711139407690.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 41537, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220837704598818857/Image_1711139407690.png?ex=69ccdcf6&is=69cb8b76&hm=b84920a8331eb46ba4495aa3688b3dd9cc970484ed74ed2b6584867c651a4516&"}, {"id": "1220837704938422372", "filename": "Image_1711139980728.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 83652, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220837704938422372/Image_1711139980728.jpg?ex=69ccdcf6&is=69cb8b76&hm=13c580614f0d87d5416153cf48e79e05d01b4375a26bd06361150625869c4273&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220843409552445440", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.海渊之力\n狂气爆发的特效出现了3个单词，vrachten、dagonff和ahogog。\n\n其中【ahogog】根据拉莱耶语翻译器得出，为英语中的【biggest】big的最高级，意思有巨大的，（体积、程度、数量等）大的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:15:51.011000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220843408965242910", "filename": "Image_1711141074888.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 43714, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220843408965242910/Image_1711141074888.png?ex=69cce246&is=69cb90c6&hm=c94c4c3ecca39239ce205ac4f2a75597c07180d10cad19591c6250144d5599bd&"}, {"id": "1220843409296851105", "filename": "Image_1711141817124.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 501846, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220843409296851105/Image_1711141817124.png?ex=69cce246&is=69cb90c6&hm=38b00d8b6e49c9d91daf5e6c6d468a24a71eab35f040d19473566625a30e8b14&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220843559066800198", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "而其他两个则是合成词的合成词。\n我们先从简单的入手。\n从表面上看，dagonff中很明显能看出dagon这个单词，也就是大衮，结合戈利亚原型大衮，我们找到了以下资料：", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:16:26.658000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220843558777524395", "filename": "Image_1711141570789.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 114802, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220843558777524395/Image_1711141570789.jpg?ex=69cce26a&is=69cb90ea&hm=652dd49005e7548efce1cf771aaad9745ae1c456ef732107d4d0f78475d43ec5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220844690333765644", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们可以从这句话的最后找到vrachten和dagonff这两个单词各自的部分，也就是：vra chten dagon ff。", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:20:56.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220844690262458478", "filename": "Image_1711141556670.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2855, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220844690262458478/Image_1711141556670.jpg?ex=69cce378&is=69cb91f8&hm=e6804db4d44115de533e3cc8ab4baadbbfca256a44cb3c612e8979c4347c7911&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220845442317680781", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "顺便插入一段科普（？）：\n大衮(Dagon)是美国小说家霍华德·菲利普·洛夫克拉夫特所创造的克苏鲁神话中的旧日支配者之一。在神话中，大衮与海德拉(Hydra)作为旧日支配者克苏鲁(Cthulhu)的从者而存在，它们为深潜者(Deep Ones)的首领、父神以及母神。\n\n在游戏中，角色原型分别对应：\n戈利亚（大衮）\n弥利亚姆（海德拉）\n凯刻斯（深潜者）", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:23:55.660000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1220847856320118836", "channel_id": "1210594811363594350", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "4.巨刃之威\n此卡为狂气爆发的延伸卡牌，力量会在此卡上发挥2倍效果且视为打击。\n狂气爆发获得力量，而巨刃之威对所有敌人造成2倍力量伤害。\n释放技能时，戈利亚挥舞巨刃时文字汇集在巨刃上，想必这也代表了他的决心。\n不过文字中依旧少了一个h，可能依旧出于其他考虑，比如美观度等。\n原文：n’gai,n’gha’ghaa\n游戏：n’gai,n’ga’ghaa", "timestamp": "2024-03-22T21:33:31.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1220847856135700480", "filename": "Image_1711142681907.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 36520, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1210594811363594350/1220847856135700480/Image_1711142681907.jpg?ex=69cce66b&is=69cb94eb&hm=70a4171ce4dd8d36d56238323072d686d2ad31a0c722477dfd2649f608363047&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210594811363594350", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于游戏自造语：古代利莫里亚语", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
